    <item>
      <title>中国五巨头第一季度利润率缩水</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/chinas-agbank-posts-163-fall-q1-profit-2024-04-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于银行面临支持现金匮乏的房地产开发商的压力，而贷款需求仍然疲软，中国五大银行的利润率在第一季度出现萎缩。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/chinas-agbank-posts-163-fall-q1-profit-2024-04-29/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 08:43:20 GMT</pubDate>
